Class Guest

  • java.lang.Object
    • Guest

  • public class Guest
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a Guest added to the System. A Guest can check in from 0 to multiple rooms.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Li Jin Quan, Lee Jian Hao, Chen Xing Yu, Kok Jia Hui
